sources.title: Hurra Die Schwedinnen Sind Da 1978 Scarlett Gunden Bea Fiedler Corinne Brodbeck
sources.description: Nikki Moser, a blond womanizer, made a deal with the burgomaster. He gave him money to buy a hotel, and for this Nikki should marry his daughter Marianne. German language with English optional subtitles
